tion>感谢 Jessica Livingston 和 Michael Nielsen 阅读本文草稿。</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Jun 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>创始人模式</title><link>https://gusangciren.github.io/blog/pg-founder-mode/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://gusangciren.github.io/blog/pg-founder-mode/</guid><description>感谢 Brian Chesky、Patrick Collison、Ron Conway、Jessica Livingston、Elon Musk、Ryan Petersen、Harj Taggar 和 Garry Tan 阅读本文草稿。</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>好文章</title><link>https://gusangciren.github.io/blog/pg-good-writing/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://gusangciren.github.io/blog/pg-good-writing/</guid><description>感谢 Jessica Livingston 和 Courtenay Pipkin 阅读本文草稿。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 May 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>正确的固执类型</title><link>https://gusangciren.github.io/blog/pg-persistence/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://gusangciren.github.io/blog/pg-persistence/</guid><description>感谢 Trevor Blackwell、Jessica Livingston、Jackie McDonough、Courtenay Pipkin、Harj Taggar 和 Garry Tan 阅读本文草稿。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Reddit 们</title><link>https://gusangciren.github.io/blog/pg-reddits/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://gusangciren.github.io/blog/pg-reddits/</guid><pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>何时做你热爱的事</title><link>https://gusangciren.github.io/blog/pg-when/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://gusangciren.github.io/blog/pg-when/</guid><description>**原文链接：** https://www.paulgraham.com/when.html</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>觉醒主义的起源</title><link>https://gusangciren.github.io/blog/pg-woke/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://gusangciren.github.io/blog/pg-woke/</guid><description>**原文链接：** https://www.paulgraham.com/woke.html</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>会写和不会写的人</title><link>https://gusangciren.github.io/blog/pg-writes/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://gusangciren.github.io/blog/pg-writes/</guid><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>可变现产品的正确思路</title><link>https://gusangciren.github.io/blog/product-for-monetization/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://gusangciren.github.io/blog/product-for-monetization/</guid><description>读者不要能力，要结果。产品是客户梦想结果以及解决方案的包装。人们的不是想买四分之一英寸的钻头，而是想要一个四分之一英寸的洞。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>如果你能坚持每周都发布一篇文章，那么……</title><link>https://gusangciren.github.io/blog/publish-weekly-4-weeks-results/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://gusangciren.github.io/blog/publish-weekly-4-weeks-results/</guid><description>四周周更带来的三个核心收益：商业闭环（迷你数字产品+最小用户）、认知升级（费曼学习法+深度思考）、心理资产（克服恐惧+建立自信）。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>真正的销售不是说服，是解决问题</title><link>https://gusangciren.github.io/blog/sales-is-problem-solving/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://gusangciren.github.io/blog/sales-is-problem-solving/</guid><description>销售创造价值，不是零和博弈。好的销售是帮别人解决问题，实现双赢</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>你讨厌的销售，我是怎么理解的？</title><link>https://gusangciren.github.io/blog/understand-sales/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://gusangciren.github.io/blog/understand-sales/</guid><description>每个人都在销售，却讨厌销售标签。三种认知偏差造成这种讨厌：不理解财富本质、忽视销售者创造的综合价值、不理解产品是客户梦想的包装。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>你在使用 AI，还是在被 AI &apos;截肢&apos;？</title><link>https://gusangciren.github.io/blog/using-ai-or-ai-amputating-you/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://gusangciren.github.io/blog/using-ai-or-ai-amputating-you/</guid><description>AI表面是效率革命，实际是在给自己装假肢。真正把AI利用得出奇高效的人，恰恰是基本功扎实的那批人。寻找捷径的人，最后走的路反而越长。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>坚持每周写一篇文章，一年后会发生什么</title><link>https://gusangciren.github.io/blog/what-happens-when-you-publish-weekly/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://gusangciren.github.io/blog/what-happens-when-you-publish-weekly/</guid><description>坚持每周发布一篇文章，不仅仅是习惯问题，而是你如何用内容构建个人资产</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>我不是鼓励写作，我在鼓励思考</title><link>https://gusangciren.github.io/blog/writing-is-thinking/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://gusangciren.github.io/blog/writing-is-thinking/</guid><description>写作强大的地方不在于记录，而在于强制把模糊的念头变成清晰的文字——这个过程本身就是思考。写清楚了，就无需记住了。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>